from tiger to demon.

129
00:05:45,145 --> 00:05:47,546
- All residents...
- Hero #1: See what I mean?

130
00:05:47,614 --> 00:05:48,747
Announcer:
...Please evacuate immediately.

131
00:05:48,816 --> 00:05:49,682
Hero #1: Hey!

132
00:05:49,750 --> 00:05:51,283
Announcer: I repeat,

133
00:05:51,351 --> 00:05:55,353
