I'll run for it as soon as--

157
00:06:47,141 --> 00:06:48,874
whaah!

158
00:06:51,745 --> 00:06:54,079
What the hell happened?

159
00:06:54,081 --> 00:06:57,015
( Groans ) I can't feel my body.

160
00:06:57,084 --> 00:06:58,884
( Groans )

161
00:07:00,754 --> 00:07:03,489
( Deep sea king chuckles )

162
00:07:03,557 --> 00:07:04,690
Lightning Max: Damn it.

163
00:07:04,758 --> 00:07:07,126
Arrogant guppy.

164
00:07:08,762 --> 00:07:12,898
Lightning flying backwards
roundhouse kick!

165
00:07:30,451 --> 00:07:32,851
Hero #4: I'm the class-s hero,

166
00:07:32,920 --> 00:07:34,986
puri-puri prisoner.

167
00:07:35,055 --> 00:07:37,589
