just to see you.

168
00:07:37,591 --> 00:07:39,057
- Sonic: Well, well.
- Puri-puri prisoner: Hmm?

169
00:07:39,126 --> 00:07:40,993
Sonic: Imagine that,

170
00:07:41,061 --> 00:07:43,796
a hero serving time in prison.

171
00:07:43,864 --> 00:07:47,666
I took a cue from you
and decided to escape as well.

172
00:07:47,735 --> 00:07:49,000
Thanks for that.

173
00:07:49,069 --> 00:07:51,669
Puri-puri prisoner:
Prisoner number 4188.

174
00:07:51,739 --> 00:07:53,672
- The name's Sonic, right?
- Sonic: Hmm?

175
00:07:53,741 --> 00:07:55,073
Puri-puri prisoner:
You surprised I know?

176
00:07:55,142 --> 00:07:57,876
I check up on all the boys
who catch my eye.

177
00:07:57,878 --> 00:07:59,144
I'm serving a life sentence

178
00:07:59,213 --> 00:08:01,413
'cause I can't seem
to control myself.

179
00:08:01,482 --> 00:08:03,815
I see a beautiful man,
and I take him.

180
00:08:03,884 --> 00:08:04,883
Deep sea king: Well, well.

181
00:08:04,952 --> 00:08:07,085
