182
00:08:07,087 --> 00:08:09,687
Goodness.
My fins are quivering.

183
00:08:09,757 --> 00:08:11,623
( Laughs )

184
00:08:13,293 --> 00:08:15,761
Puri-puri prisoner: My!
I feel the strength

185
00:08:15,763 --> 00:08:17,162
