186
00:08:17,231 --> 00:08:18,831
Hang back, Sonic, dear

187
00:08:18,833 --> 00:08:20,165
( deep sea king laughing )

188
00:08:20,167 --> 00:08:22,634
Class a, rank 11, sweet stinger

189
00:08:22,703 --> 00:08:24,903
and class a, rank 20,
lightning Max,

190
00:08:24,972 --> 00:08:28,173
I fancied
both of those lovelies.

191
00:08:28,241 --> 00:08:31,176
Then you show up out of nowhere
and ruin them!

192
00:08:31,245 --> 00:08:34,780
Now that genos passed me,
I rank lowest in my class,

193
00:08:34,848 --> 00:08:36,915
but I'm still class s,

194
00:08:36,984 --> 00:08:39,251
unlike those two
you've defeated.

195
00:08:39,319 --> 00:08:41,586
I'll start things off
at half power

