197
00:08:43,657 --> 00:08:46,058
( Yells )

198
00:08:46,126 --> 00:08:47,226
( Gasps )

199
00:08:50,130 --> 00:08:51,596
Raah!

200
00:08:51,665 --> 00:08:53,865
You made me rip
the hand-knit sweater

201
00:08:53,934 --> 00:08:57,202
