202
00:08:57,271 --> 00:09:03,074
I will never forgive you,
you bastard!

203
00:09:03,144 --> 00:09:04,542
Deep sea king: Mmm.

204
00:09:04,612 --> 00:09:07,212
A delectable slab of meat,
prime and tasty.

205
00:09:07,281 --> 00:09:10,249
You've whet my appetite.

206
00:09:12,886 --> 00:09:14,686
( Puri-puri prisoner grunts )

207
00:09:14,755 --> 00:09:16,822
( Growls )

208
00:09:16,890 --> 00:09:18,357
Deep sea king: Huh?

209
00:09:18,359 --> 00:09:19,291
Oh, dear.

210
00:09:26,233 --> 00:09:27,833
Deep sea king: I felt that...

211
00:09:27,901 --> 00:09:29,234
( Bones pop )

212
00:09:29,303 --> 00:09:30,569
Just a little.

213
00:09:30,637 --> 00:09:32,838
Puri-puri prisoner:
I felt that as well,

214
00:09:32,906 --> 00:09:34,773
a little. ( Snorts )

215
00:09:36,110 --> 00:09:37,709
Sonic: Puri-puri prisoner
is acting tough,

216
00:09:37,711 --> 00:09:39,578
but I can tell
that he's hurting.

217
00:09:39,646 --> 00:09:42,914
So this is what a fight
between a demon-level monster

218
00:09:42,983 --> 00:09:45,050
and a class-s hero looks like?

219
00:09:45,052 --> 00:09:46,585
It's almost comical.

220
00:09:46,653 --> 00:09:49,654
Neither one of them
could defeat me.

221
00:09:49,723 --> 00:09:51,122
Puri-puri prisoner: Damn it.

222
00:09:51,192 --> 00:09:53,659
His punch was stronger
than I expected.

223
00:09:53,727 --> 00:09:55,994
