228
00:10:05,339 --> 00:10:07,539
Ready.

229
00:10:07,608 --> 00:10:09,341
Transform!

230
00:10:09,409 --> 00:10:10,942
Deep sea king: Huh?

231
00:10:11,011 --> 00:10:16,347
Puri-puri prisoner:
Puri-puri prisoner, angel style!

232
00:10:16,417 --> 00:10:20,085
Sonic: He's naked,
and he's definitely no angel,

233
00:10:20,154 --> 00:10:22,020
