234
00:10:22,022 --> 00:10:24,289
Nor do I want to watch.
I'm outta here.

235
00:10:24,291 --> 00:10:26,291
Puri-puri prisoner:
No one's seen my angel style

236
00:10:26,359 --> 00:10:28,427
