about it, fish man.

237
00:10:28,429 --> 00:10:30,962
Sonic:
All the more reason to leave.

238
00:10:31,031 --> 00:10:33,698
Deep sea king: Quite unsightly.

239
00:10:33,768 --> 00:10:35,634
Puri-puri prisoner: Are those...

