256
00:11:31,158 --> 00:11:32,290
Hear me.

257
00:11:32,359 --> 00:11:35,027
The objective
of a combination move

258
00:11:35,029 --> 00:11:36,895
is to finish your opponent.

259
00:11:36,963 --> 00:11:40,965
